{"tid":1953374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(有鬼?) 大埔警署被掟5枚汽油彈　警拘捕3名男中學生","createTime":"2020-04-01T07:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T14:06:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5f98fac2696ad034dfe63d67300afa20423b0cbf","tid":1953374,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"大埔警署於今日(1日)凌晨時分，被人投擲汽油彈縱火，警方拘捕3名男子。大埔警區助理指揮官(刑事)莊逸成表示，案發2時40分，警署的汽車出入口位置被掟汽油彈，3枚落入警署內大地，2枚在警署外着陸，<span style=\"color: red;\">埋伏的警員立刻採取行動，拘捕3名男子，當中2人一度反抗，亦涉嫌襲警被捕</span>。3名被捕男子(16至18歲)，為就讀同一間中學的學生，行動仍在繼續，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200401/bkn-20200401142632325-0401_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0cf5be8c1df66493af21e78005596ae3db986267","tid":1953374,"uid":101507,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:02:36.000Z","msg":"大地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 着陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫依段野嗰條友到底識唔識中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5e686e501391ad8a83667615e3bb2a8620bcc1","tid":1953374,"uid":303450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"大地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119102eb9fd7ceef79fd6bfba87185f0c508c0fa","tid":1953374,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:03:55.000Z","msg":"香港真係無得救"},{"pid":"d5b1ff09f26d0b7807b4eef0dfd4cd248af6bcc1","tid":1953374,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"人地應該日日埋伏"},{"pid":"44a86b688fcccd224522e7f27e60f8e0fc1e43f6","tid":1953374,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c5e686e501391ad8a83667615e3bb2a862